oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The AFA is a diverse, environmentallyaware group; so is Seattle. Hence, it isappropriate that our 1987 convention isbeing hosted by Seattle.Seattle is the " Emerald City" of the" Evergreen State" (Washington). It is amany-faceted city of space, simpleelegance, magic, and natural beauty - ajewel.Visitors are astonished at the lushgreenery and the wealth of natural beautyin and around Seattle. Literally touchingthe city's boundaries are thousands ofsquare miles of evergreen forest andhundreds of miles of salt and freshwatershoreline. The views of mountains andwater are spectacular.
